{"tid":855541,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搞咁多,解決唔到保皇狗佔大多數 咪又係晒氣","createTime":"2018-10-10T06:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T01:48:09.000Z","uid":38523,"like":26,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f976eae881c8e5b5c6e701aab55a11ccce246e35","tid":855541,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"所以你地依加知點解關愛座hunter搞咁多花樣都唔搞保皇狗啦<br />\n因為佢知道出去抗爭又好行街又好乜都好<br />\n只要保皇狗佔大多數<br />\n就食硬你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩叫實際咩叫做樣<br />\n你地都唔知？<br />\n依加係度叫春有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dc99e3d90560d2fb563f0fb7bb70bdd9a48c04","tid":855541,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"一個係雨革完即刻番大陸做四年野<br />\n做完番來即加入學聯<br />\n不停屌保皇狗以外既政黨放生保皇狗<br />\n咁樣你地都睇唔穿<br />\n依加叫春？<br />\n笑死我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/140942_e0186b7febae4fc2be72157d91c7ff78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F140942_e0186b7febae4fc2be72157d91c7ff78.png&h=9156ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/140948_99f4a28b98e36d992b990ec18800c180.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F140948_99f4a28b98e36d992b990ec18800c180.png&h=46f3d15e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3336cea9ab828df5cc85ac4aff44aea02c1c6808","tid":855541,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"我知有班人實入來話呢個時勢仲講呢d有咩用之類架<br />\n但我一早已經叫左你地主力保皇狗<br />\n你地要聽關狗呢個大陸教師比佢分散力量<br />\n係你地抵死<br />\n唔係我依加講呢d冇用<br />\n而係你地已經錯失最好時機了<br />\n多謝關愛座hunter啦<br />\n你依加睇番佢所作所為<br />\n就睇得出佢樣樣都全力屌<br />\n就係保皇狗放生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f74ab7b1dd69e70abfc399b1c208a659ee11cf","tid":855541,"uid":38523,"like":3,"disli